Package: jagsUI
Version: 0.01-7
Date: 2014-5-12
Title: Run JAGS from R (a wrapper for rjags)
Author: Ken Kellner <ken@kenkellner.com>
Maintainer: Ken Kellner <ken@kenkellner.com>
Depends: R (>= 2.14.0), rjags (>= 3-3), parallel
Imports: rjags, coda (>= 0.13), parallel
SystemRequirements: JAGS (http://mcmc-jags.sourceforge.net)
Description: This package provides a straightforward user interface for running JAGS analyses from within R, via rjags. The goals of jagsUI are to be simple, easy to learn, and frequently updated. 
URL: http://code.kenkellner.com/jagsui
NeedsCompilation: no
